<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الطَّائِفَتِيْنِ}</span> ... عِيرِ قُرَيْشٍ، وَمَا تَحْمِلُهُ مِنْ أَرْزَاقٍ، أَوِ النَّفِيرِ لِقِتَالِهِمْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذَاتِ الشَّوْكَةِ}</span> ... صَاحِبَةِ السِّلَاحِ، وَالْقُوَّةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيَقْطَعَ}</span> ... يَسْتَاصِلَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{دَابِرَ الْكَافِرِينَ}</span> ... آخِرَهُمْ،<span class="c5"> وَالْمُرَادُ:</span> جَمِيعُهُمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُرْدِفِينَ}</span> ... يَتْبَعُ بَعْضُهُمْ بَعْضًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُغَشِّيكُمُ}</span> ... يُلْقِي النُّعَاسَ عَلَيْكُمْ؛ كَالْغِطَاءِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَمَنَةً}</span> ... أَمَانًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
